WEBVTT

00:00:00.581 --> 00:00:04.289
I'm a man who's trying to live from his heart,

00:00:04.289 --> 00:00:07.354
and so just before I get going,

00:00:07.354 --> 00:00:09.925
I wanted to tell you as a South African

00:00:09.925 --> 00:00:12.909
that one of the men who has inspired me most

00:00:12.909 --> 00:00:15.975
passed away a few hours ago.

00:00:15.975 --> 00:00:18.665
Nelson Mandela has come to the end

00:00:18.665 --> 00:00:21.345
of his long walk to freedom.

00:00:21.345 --> 00:00:26.280
And so this talk is going to be for him.

00:00:28.544 --> 00:00:31.354
I grew up in wonder.